                                    <li class="p" value="3">
                                        <p>Fare clic su <img src="../Resources/Images/dbllistbox/arrowdx_on.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;width: 54px;height: 19px;" width="54" height="19" border="0" /> 
